```

**Quality bar**: Every deliverable MUST have acceptance criteria. Vague deliverables like "improve the code" are not acceptable — make them specific and testable.

**Design depth bar**: The plan MUST include Alternatives Considered, Key Interfaces, and Retrospective Anchors. `harness plan-lint` enforces System Design Thinking and Design Principles as hard errors.
